The <strong>WebGLShader</strong> is part of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API">WebGL API</a> and can either be a vertex or a fragment shader. A <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLProgram" title="The WebGLProgram is part of the WebGL API and is a combination of two compiled WebGLShaders consisting of a vertex shader and a fragment shader (both written in GLSL). These are then linked into a usable program."><code>WebGLProgram</code></a> requires both types of shaders.